premise_source_doc_sentence: As the only son of Edmund G. `` Pat '' Brown Sr. , the 32nd governor of California  (  1959 -- 1967  )  , Jerry Brown began his political career as a member of the Los Angeles Community College District Board of Trustees  (  1969 -- 1971  )  , before serving as Secretary of State of California  (  1971 -- 1975  )  .
